# Update .claude/contexts/story-{story_id}/progress.md

## Completed Tasks
- [x] {COMPLETED_TASK_1} - {DATE}
- [x] {COMPLETED_TASK_2} - {DATE}

## Technical Decisions
- {DECISION_1}: {REASONING}
- {DECISION_2}: {REASONING}

## Files Modified
- {FILE_PATH_1} - {CHANGE_DESCRIPTION}
- {FILE_PATH_2} - {CHANGE_DESCRIPTION}

step.commands:

# Stage all changes
git add .

# Commit with conventional commit message
git commit -m "feat: {STORY_TITLE}

- {CHANGE_1}
- {CHANGE_2}
- {CHANGE_3}

Closes #{STORY_NUMBER}"

# Push changes git push origin feature/story-{STORY_NUMBER}-{BRIEF_DESCRIPTION}
# Create PR gh pr create \ --title "feat: {STORY_TITLE}" \ --body "## Summary
Implements #{STORY_NUMBER} - {STORY_DESCRIPTION}
## Changes - {DETAILED_CHANGE_1} - {DETAILED_CHANGE_2} - {DETAILED_CHANGE_3}
## Testing - ✅ All unit tests passing - ✅ Integration tests added - ✅ Manual testing completed
## Checklist - [x] Tests written and passing - [x] TypeScript types complete (no 'any') - [x] Documentation updated - [x] Lint and format checks pass - [x] Security standards followed (RLS, validation) - [x] Performance acceptable - [x] Accessibility standards met (WCAG 2.1 AA)
## Screenshots (if applicable) {ADD_SCREENSHOTS_IF_UI_CHANGES}" \ --assignee @me \ --label "ready-for-review"

# PR creation auto-moves story to "Review" column # Update implementation phase gh issue edit {STORY_NUMBER} \ --add-field "Implementation Phase=Review"
# Add completion comment gh issue comment {STORY_NUMBER} \ --body "✅ Implementation complete and PR created: #{PR_NUMBER}
**Session End**: $(date) **Quality Checks**: All passing **Ready for**: Code review"

